1
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:58,799
Who are you looking for?

2
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:02,960
Welcome, honored guest.

3
00:01:02,960 --> 00:01:04,039
I apologize for not greeting you earlier.

4
00:01:04,960 --> 00:01:05,960
Who are you?

5
00:01:06,359 --> 00:01:07,400
I am Bai Weiran,

6
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,879
the owner of this humble money house.

7
00:01:09,359 --> 00:01:10,840
Your Highness,

8
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:11,680
what brings you here?

9
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,680
I suspect this place

10
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:17,560
is more than just a simple money house.

11
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:19,959
Since Meng Li's arrival,

12
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:20,959
no one else has come in or out.

13
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:22,040
Now she's gone.

14
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:23,680
There must be something fishy.

15
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:25,920
It seems

16
00:01:26,319 --> 00:01:28,239
your bank holds many secrets.

17
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,519
Your Highness,

18
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:36,359
every transaction here is confidential.

19
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:37,799
What would you like to know?

20
00:01:38,239 --> 00:01:39,040
I want her alive

21
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,159
or dead!

22
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,480
She vanished into thin air.

23
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:43,519
If not a witch, then what?

24
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:46,120
If I don't see her today,

25
00:01:47,319 --> 00:01:48,079
you

26
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:50,319
and this bank

27
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,359
will be doomed.

28
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:03,280
Boss Bai,

29
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,159
I've sorted out the account books.

30
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,199
Your Highness.

31
00:02:20,599 --> 00:02:21,280
Your Highness,

32
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,159
why are you here?

33
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:23,439
I should be asking you that.

34
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,479
Why are you here?

35
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:27,599
In a few days,

36
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:30,479
it will be the seventh day after their death.

37
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,039
I borrowed some money

38
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,159
from Boss Bai.

39
00:02:34,479 --> 00:02:35,680
To show my gratitude,

40
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:37,159
I helped him tidy up the warehouse.

41
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:42,520
Miss Meng,

42
00:02:42,759 --> 00:02:44,039
take this money.

43
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,080
No need to repay in a hurry.

44
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,400
Thank you, Boss Bai.

45
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,000
Shopkeeper Bai,

46
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,680
you're so generous.

47
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,960
Willing to lend so much money

48
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,759
to someone you barely know.

49
00:03:03,919 --> 00:03:05,759
Charity brings wealth.

50
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,599
Harming the innocent

51
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,960
brings retribution.

52
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:15,360
[Crap!]

53
00:03:15,599 --> 00:03:16,919
[The Holy Chain is gone.]

54
00:03:23,879 --> 00:03:25,000
You are a demon.

55
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,560
I...

56
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,039
Demon!

57
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,039
If Your Highness

58
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,439
insists on that,

59
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:49,680
I can't defend myself.

60
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,159
But that's just your belief,

61
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:53,680
not reality.

62
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,520
Miss Meng,

63
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:56,039
His Highness is just and fair.

64
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:57,280
He wouldn't kill innocent people.

65
00:04:00,240 --> 00:04:00,800
Your Highness,

66
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,800
a demon did pass by here.

67
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,560
The demon hunter has gone to deal with it.

68
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,719
Shopkeeper Bai,

69
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:14,879
I'm sorry to bother you.

70
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:16,400
Meng Li,

71
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,519
come back with me.

72
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,480
[He's suspicious.]

73
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:40,560
[It's dangerous to stay around him.]

74
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:44,240
[I must make him fall in love with me soon,]

75
00:04:44,480 --> 00:04:45,759
[so that he won't suspect me.]

76
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,120
Why don't you go to bed?

77
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,800
I can't fall asleep when you're awake.

78
00:04:51,879 --> 00:04:53,040
[In that case,]

79
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:55,160
[I have to make a move.]

80
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:33,279
You can't hold back anymore.

81
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:35,560
Your Highness,

82
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,120
it's late at night.

83
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:39,360
I just

84
00:05:39,519 --> 00:05:41,160
want you to go to bed.

85
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,160
To escort me back?

86
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:46,920
Yet you hold a sharp hairpin.

87
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:50,199
What are your intentions?

88
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:55,120
Only you know the truth.

89
00:05:56,079 --> 00:05:57,639
If you don't trust me,

90
00:05:59,000 --> 00:06:00,399
why not just kill me?

91
00:06:00,959 --> 00:06:02,319
Do you think I wouldn't dare?

92
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,160
Your Highness.

93
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:12,759
Speak.

94
00:06:12,759 --> 00:06:15,240
Senior Mu has spotted demons on Nether Mountain.

95
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,360
She's set up a barrier.

96
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:18,040
Awaiting your order.

97
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:18,839
Assemble the troops.

98
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,399
We'll set off immediately.

99
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:21,240
Yes.

100
00:06:56,319 --> 00:06:57,000
No!

101
00:06:57,079 --> 00:06:58,000
It's an illusion!

102
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,879
Go to hell!

103
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,319
Now,

104
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,160
will you trust me?

105
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,600
How did you get here?

106
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,120
I've been following you

107
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:15,240
since you left the mansion.

108
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,320
I told you,

109
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:20,519
I also want to avenge my master and brother.

110
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:21,879
Gather the team.

111
00:09:22,159 --> 00:09:23,240
We leave immediately.

112
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,840
Yes, sir.

113
00:09:27,679 --> 00:09:28,480
Your Highness,

114
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,080
can I come with you?

115
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,960
I also want to avenge my master and brother.

116
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,320
But Your Highness

117
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:40,879
doesn't think I can do it.

118
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,639
I'll prove to you

119
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,120
with my actions.

120
00:09:45,559 --> 00:09:47,080
He's lost his true form,

121
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,759
though she inhabits Yue Shu's body,

122
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,360
her soul will soon disperse.

123
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,120
She's taken the Soul-borrowing Pearl.

124
00:09:52,399 --> 00:09:54,639
Her demon power will surge at death,

125
00:09:54,799 --> 00:09:56,440
allowing her to transform into a fox

126
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,600
and help you finish this grand finale.

127
00:09:59,039 --> 00:10:01,559
Demon hunters know the clan's law.

128
00:10:02,120 --> 00:10:04,240
This is the only way to dispel Shen Que's

129
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:06,039
doubts about your identity.

130
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,559
I'd rather not risk A-He's life

131
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,840
if not absolutely necessary.

132
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:11,159
But the clan's survival hangs in the balance.

133
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,840
I have no choice.

134
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,600
[The Iron Law of the Demon Race]

135
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,200
[forbids killing each other.]

136
00:10:17,519 --> 00:10:18,399
[It seems]

137
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:20,440
[I've misunderstood her.]

138
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:24,960
It's getting late,

139
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,120
and the mist is thick.

140
00:10:26,679 --> 00:10:28,799
Let's rest in the hut ahead.

141
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,440
We'll return to the mansion

142
00:10:31,039 --> 00:10:31,879
when the mist clears.

143
00:10:36,360 --> 00:10:37,559
A-He, just watch.

144
00:10:38,399 --> 00:10:41,240
I'll make these cruel, hypocritical mortals pay.

145
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,360
[for your sacrifice.]

146
00:10:49,200 --> 00:10:50,240
It's cold

147
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,759
and damp in the mountains.

148
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,279
Your Highness, let me dry your clothes.

149
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,080
Don't catch a cold.

150
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:18,080
[Shen Que is so protective of this.]

151
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:22,039
[It must mean a lot to him.]

152
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:24,120
[This is a good opportunity]

153
00:11:25,039 --> 00:11:26,840
[for me.]

154
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,120
Your Highness.

155
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:42,720
Let me help you.

156
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,360
Done?

157
00:12:36,159 --> 00:12:37,120
Let me

158
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,000
clean the bead for you.

159
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,279
You

160
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,519
cherish it so much.

161
00:12:53,559 --> 00:12:55,559
Is it a gift from someone you love?

162
00:12:56,639 --> 00:12:57,720
It's the only thing

163
00:12:59,279 --> 00:13:00,519
my brother left me.

164
00:13:03,279 --> 00:13:04,720
Your brother?

165
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:07,720
He must have been very good to you.

166
00:13:11,879 --> 00:13:13,799
My mother died when I was young,

167
00:13:14,879 --> 00:13:16,240
and my father was too busy

168
00:13:16,639 --> 00:13:17,960
with state affairs to care for me.

169
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,840
Among my brothers,

170
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,200
only he cared for me.

171
00:13:23,519 --> 00:13:24,519
He taught me to ride and shoot,

172
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:25,679
read and write,

173
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,159
and how to navigate the world.

174
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:28,399
And then?

175
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:31,799
Then...

176
00:13:35,120 --> 00:13:36,600
When he died,

177
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:38,720
I wasn't in the palace.

178
00:13:42,039 --> 00:13:43,360
He was killed by dark forces,

179
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:45,240
his death was gruesome.
